{"commentv2": 1, "number": 40, "id": 965490, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Fylwind", "body": "If you are a shaman and would like to solo this guy, make sure you are level 20+ to get Water Shield. With Water Shield, Lesser Healing Wave, and Wind Shear, soloing him is just a matter of slowly dpsing him down while keeping yourself alive. Tremor totem works wonders here too for his Fear effect.", "date": "2010-02-04T08:02:21-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
